From 5204aeebeb5def96e0f0e1bd439ef2e1a8ae1852 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 17 Jul 2025 15:01:18 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 5/7] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:HOSTAPD: Add support for building and 
 sending Unsolicited DSCP policy request

Add support to construct and transmit unsolicited DSCP
Policy Request frames to connected STAs. This includes:

Constructs a QoS Policy element for a given DSCP policy,
including qos management attributes like classifier,
domain name, and port range.

Builds and sends one or more DSCP Policy Request frames to a STA,
handling fragmentation if the total size exceeds the maximum allowed.

Add Support for batching multiple policies and setting the More bit
when additional frames are needed.

Patch-dependency:None
Tag: DAP

Signed-off-by: Aishwarya R <aisr@qti.qualcomm.com>
